  "original_title": "\u0dbb\u0dd4\u0dc3\u0dd2\u0dba\u0dcf\u0dc0\u0dda\u0db1\u0dca \u0dc3\u0dd4\u0db6\u0daf\u0dcf\u0dba\u0dd2 \u0db4\u0dca\u200d\u0dbb\u0d9a\u0dcf\u0dc1\u0dba\u0d9a\u0dca",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "A positive statement from Russia",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "The Ambassador of the Russian Federation to Sri Lanka Mr. Yuri Materi said that Russia's support will be provided to Sri Lanka.",
        "Russian Ambassador to Sri Lanka Yuri Materi called on Foreign Minister Prof. GL Peiris.",
        "Several issues have been discussed in the hope of strengthening multi-faceted bilateral relations. Prof. G. L. Peiris informed Ambassador Uri Materi about the steps taken to overcome the economic crisis that Sri Lanka is facing.",
        "It has also been stated in the meeting with Mr. Ambassador Uri Materi that they have worked with close cooperation regarding the unfinished engagements to further strengthen the bilateral relations between Sri Lanka and Russia."
      ],
